华特迪士尼公司在[[中国|中国]]的两处[[主题公园|主题公园]]——[[香港迪士尼乐园|香港迪士尼乐园]]和[[上海迪士尼乐园|上海迪士尼乐园]]在2020年1月25日宣布关闭<ref>{{cite web |title=New virus mutes Lunar New Year celebrations worldwide |url=https://apnews.com/article/10e22bef65d8e1a85ba0c1761c3ea711 |publisher=[[美联社|美联社]] |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104185153/https://apnews.com/article/10e22bef65d8e1a85ba0c1761c3ea711 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Shanghai Disney shuts to prevent spread of virus |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/01/24/shanghai-disney-shuts-to-prevent-spread-of-virus.html |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |publisher=[[路透社|路透社]] |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2020-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126022835/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/01/24/shanghai-disney-shuts-to-prevent-spread-of-virus.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月28日，位于[[日本|日本]]的[[东京迪士尼度假区|东京迪士尼度假区]]也宣布关闭<ref>{{cite web |title=Tokyo Disneyland to close through mid-March on coronavirus concerns |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/28/tokyo-disneyland-to-close-through-mid-march-on-coronavirus-concerns.html |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |publisher=[[路透社|路透社]] |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116161423/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/28/tokyo-disneyland-to-close-through-mid-march-on-coronavirus-concerns.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月12日，[[迪士尼乐园度假区|迪士尼乐园度假区]]、[[华特迪士尼世界度假区|华特迪士尼世界度假区]]和[[巴黎迪士尼乐园度假区|巴黎迪士尼乐园度假区]]也宣布将从3月15日开始最少关闭至当月月底，而这标志着迪士尼公司旗下的全球六大主题主题公园都首次关闭<ref>{{cite web |author1=Elaine Low |title=Disneyland and Walt Disney World Now Indefinitely Closed Amid Coronavirus Outbreak |url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/disneyland-walt-disney-world-closed-indefinitely-coronavirus-outbreak-1203547472/ |publisher=[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]] |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116161245/https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/disneyland-walt-disney-world-closed-indefinitely-coronavirus-outbreak-1203547472/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。两天后，迪士尼公司再次宣布暂停其实习计划，这包括了{{Link-en|迪士尼学院项目|Disney College Program}}和{{Link-en|迪士尼国际项目|Disney International Programs|国际项目}}<ref>{{cite web |author1=Ashley Carter |title=Disney College Program to be Suspended, Participants Sent Home |url=https://www.mynews13.com/fl/orlando/news/2020/03/14/disney-college-program-to-be-suspended--participants-sent-home |publisher=Spectrum News |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116161235/https://www.mynews13.com/fl/orlando/news/2020/03/14/disney-college-program-to-be-suspended--participants-sent-home |dead-url=no }}</ref>；随后暂停被宣布延长至2020年年底<ref>{{cite web |title=Disney College Program suspended until further notice at Disneyland, Walt Disney World |url=https://attractionsmagazine.com/disney-college-program-suspended-until-further-notice-disneyland-disney-world/ |publisher=Attractions Magazine |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116161343/https://attractionsmagazine.com/disney-college-program-suspended-until-further-notice-disneyland-disney-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

